  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Picture this: you and your buddies are <strong>playing soccer</strong>, but you're all <strong>drunk</strong> as skunks. And not just any old drunk, I'm talking falling-down, can't walk straight, pissing your pants drunk. Sounds like a blast, right? Well, that's exactly what Drunken FC is all about.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You got these <strong>sixteen characters</strong> that are all goofy and cartoony, with some crazy-ass moves that'll have you rollin' on the floor. And the <strong>physics-based gameplay</strong> means there's no animation, it's all about real, unpredictable, and hilarious movements. You'll be bumping, crashing, and falling all over the place, trying to score goals on <strong>four different levels</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's no story or anything, just straight-up <strong>action</strong> and <strong>laughs</strong>. So, if you're looking for a party game that'll have you and your friends cracking up for hours, Drunken FC is the way to go. Get it now, and let's get <strong>drunk</strong> on football! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>locally</strong>, or <strong>remotely via Steam Remote Play Together</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single player</strong> against CPU players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op, or <strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Native Xbox</strong> controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PlayStation</strong> controller support via Steam Input.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keyboard</strong> support for one local player. (Controller recommended)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invite your friends</strong> in-game via Steam Remote Play Together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/729ba237c68276a8b4e387afd52e00ae.poster.avif?t=1750326914\" width=608 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/729ba237c68276a8b4e387afd52e00ae.webm?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/729ba237c68276a8b4e387afd52e00ae.mp4?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fantastic jumps!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/18b2b2c2f7b2614ba40bf95860567c83.poster.avif?t=1750326914\" width=640 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/18b2b2c2f7b2614ba40bf95860567c83.webm?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/18b2b2c2f7b2614ba40bf95860567c83.mp4?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Epic takedowns!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/599f357cf56c82556b5101953f528844.poster.avif?t=1750326914\" width=640 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/599f357cf56c82556b5101953f528844.webm?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/599f357cf56c82556b5101953f528844.mp4?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Picture this: you and your buddies are <strong>playing soccer</strong>, but you're all <strong>drunk</strong> as skunks. And not just any old drunk, I'm talking falling-down, can't walk straight, pissing your pants drunk. Sounds like a blast, right? Well, that's exactly what Drunken FC is all about.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You got these <strong>sixteen characters</strong> that are all goofy and cartoony, with some crazy-ass moves that'll have you rollin' on the floor. And the <strong>physics-based gameplay</strong> means there's no animation, it's all about real, unpredictable, and hilarious movements. You'll be bumping, crashing, and falling all over the place, trying to score goals on <strong>four different levels</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's no story or anything, just straight-up <strong>action</strong> and <strong>laughs</strong>. So, if you're looking for a party game that'll have you and your friends cracking up for hours, Drunken FC is the way to go. Get it now, and let's get <strong>drunk</strong> on football! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>locally</strong>, or <strong>remotely via Steam Remote Play Together</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single player</strong> against CPU players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op, or <strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Native Xbox</strong> controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PlayStation</strong> controller support via Steam Input.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keyboard</strong> support for one local player. (Controller recommended)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Invite your friends</strong> in-game via Steam Remote Play Together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/729ba237c68276a8b4e387afd52e00ae.poster.avif?t=1750326914\" width=608 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/729ba237c68276a8b4e387afd52e00ae.webm?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/729ba237c68276a8b4e387afd52e00ae.mp4?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fantastic jumps!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/18b2b2c2f7b2614ba40bf95860567c83.poster.avif?t=1750326914\" width=640 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/18b2b2c2f7b2614ba40bf95860567c83.webm?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/18b2b2c2f7b2614ba40bf95860567c83.mp4?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Epic takedowns!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/599f357cf56c82556b5101953f528844.poster.avif?t=1750326914\" width=640 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1991820/extras/599f357cf56c82556b5101953f528844.webm?t=1750326914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><